clothes underneath this time.

02:36.025 --> 02:37.853
Okay, let's talk
about market strategies,
competition analysis,

02:37.896 --> 02:39.463
and a design
and development plan.

02:39.507 --> 02:42.379
Oh, Melanie,
you are a godsend.No, you're the godsend.

02:42.423 --> 02:44.468
I mean, when John left,
I thought my life was over.

02:44.512 --> 02:46.383
And now I have a friend,
a dream,

02:46.427 --> 02:49.343
and no fewer than six
tear-away business suits.

02:49.386 --> 02:51.040
Not a great use
of our capital.
Hmm.

02:51.083 --> 02:52.955
Oh, shoot. I got to go get Logan
from school.

02:52.998 --> 02:54.043
Kenneth can
go and get him.

02:54.086 --> 02:55.218
Can he?

02:55.262 --> 02:57.220
I-Is Kenneth something

02:57.264 --> 02:58.178
you can lend your friends

02:58.221 --> 03:00.484
