03:00.528 --> 03:02.530
Did you specifically
use that as an example

03:02.573 --> 03:05.228
because you've borrowed
our "Mad Men" DVD set

03:05.272 --> 03:06.577
and have as yet
to give it back?

03:08.144 --> 03:09.145
I'll go get Logan.

03:09.189 --> 03:11.234
A romance?

03:11.278 --> 03:12.279
Where do we even start?

03:14.019 --> 03:18.415
"We could draw on
our own romantic pasts."

03:22.419 --> 03:23.725
Yeah.

03:23.768 --> 03:25.814
You know, if you're
looking for romance,

03:25.857 --> 03:27.859
you should've seen me
in the planetarium earlier.

03:27.903 --> 03:29.296
This girl, Izzy,
came in,

03:29.339 --> 03:32.429
and we had
insane chemistry.

03:32.473 --> 03:34.518
And how does this help us
with our movie?

03:34.562 --> 03:36.433
You need to cast Izzy and me
as the leads.

03:36.477 --> 03:38.000
We'll fall in love,

03:38.043 --> 03:40.263
and you'll get
the best on-screen romance

03:40.307 --> 03:42.700
since a certain Harry
met the Hendersons.

03:43.919 --> 03:45.529
Sound like a plan?

03:47.183 --> 03:48.619
Sure.

03:48.663 --> 03:49.533
I'm excited, too, guys.

03:51.927 --> 03:53.102
Whoa!

03:53.145 --> 03:54.408
All those years,

03:54.451 --> 03:56.236
we have not lost
the sound.Or the look.

03:56.279 --> 03:57.585
-Wore these in '92.

03:57.628 --> 03:59.064
I had them altered.

03:59.108 --> 04:00.283
-Yeah.

04:00.327 --> 04:02.416
Hey. We got the sound
and the look.

04:02.459 --> 04:03.330
I think we should gig.

04:03.373 --> 04:05.157
Come on.
We're grown-ups now.

04:05.201 --> 04:07.116
It'd be pathetic.
This -- This is just for us.

04:07.159 --> 04:07.899
Yeah, you're right.

04:07.943 --> 04:08.857
That was a cheap escape

04:08.900 --> 04:10.293
we needed
when we were young

04:10.337 --> 04:12.252
because we had
nothing else.

04:12.295 --> 04:15.080
We were broke,
lived in crappy houses.

04:15.124 --> 04:16.517
We hated our jobs.

04:16.560 --> 04:19.084
Yeah, remember those days?

04:19.868 --> 04:22.087
-Anyhoo, "Satisfaction."
-Yes.

04:23.132 --> 04:26.614
♪ I can't get no

