♪ And I try

04:33.316 --> 04:35.100
♪ And I try

04:35.144 --> 04:36.450
♪ And I try Dylan: Whoa.

04:36.493 --> 04:37.886
You guys are amazing.

04:37.929 --> 04:39.235
Really?

04:39.279 --> 04:40.367
Yeah, I guess
we kind of are.

04:40.410 --> 04:43.326
Don't. Jimmy doesn't
need adoration.

04:43.370 --> 04:44.501
No, no, no, no, no.
Let her finish.

04:44.545 --> 04:45.546
What was that song?

04:45.589 --> 04:46.503
Uh, it's called
"Satisfaction."

