about to make some magic.

05:19.014 --> 05:21.233
Oh, yeah, and, uh,
one of us doesn't talk.

05:23.758 --> 05:26.238
Can I, uh, talk to you
over here for a sec?

05:27.936 --> 05:30.242
Don't you ever
one-up me again,

05:30.286 --> 05:31.635
especially
in front of Izzy.

05:31.679 --> 05:32.810
Sorry?

05:32.854 --> 05:34.856
No, I-I'm sorry.

05:34.899 --> 05:36.336
Same team.

05:36.379 --> 05:37.772
