work then.

09:52.853 --> 09:54.637
Ooh, about that.

09:54.681 --> 09:57.248
I was cooking up
a surprise getaway.

09:57.292 --> 09:58.772
Well, I support that.
Yeah?

09:58.815 --> 10:00.948
Yeah. Just don't take
Melanie.

10:00.991 --> 10:02.950
I'm sorry. You can't.

10:02.993 --> 10:04.908
I can't?

10:04.952 --> 10:07.215
