11:16.023 --> 11:17.502
How does that
first one go?

11:18.765 --> 11:19.940
Um...

11:19.983 --> 11:22.812
I-I can't get no...

11:22.856 --> 11:24.988
satisfaction.

11:25.032 --> 11:27.948
