11:27.991 --> 11:29.558
And they're
great performers, too.

11:29.601 --> 11:31.603
Uh, do that dance you do
during the song.

11:41.048 --> 11:42.310
Something like that.

11:42.353 --> 11:43.659
What do you
think, Dad?

11:46.880 --> 11:48.533
I think
they're fantastic.

11:49.883 --> 11:52.363
And if I hadn't just
signed a similar act,

11:52.407 --> 11:54.888
we'd be begging
to work with you.

11:56.803 --> 11:59.283
T-Thank you.
