11:59.327 --> 12:01.546
Uh, before I go,

12:01.590 --> 12:04.941
uh, I was wondering if any of
you want to play a song I wrote

12:04.985 --> 12:07.901
called "Smells Like
Teen Spirit."

12:07.944 --> 12:10.120
Sure.
