12:11.600 --> 12:12.557
Izzy's parking.

12:12.601 --> 12:13.994
Let's fix this movie.

12:14.037 --> 12:15.735
Come on, man.

12:15.778 --> 12:17.345
Just write a script
that makes me look awesome

12:17.388 --> 12:19.608
and makes her
fall in love with me.

12:19.651 --> 12:21.392
You can do it.
You're a creative genius.

12:23.003 --> 12:24.569
-Hello.
-Izzy!

12:24.613 --> 12:27.485
